**[Falcon's Response — Categorical Apology]**

**GM** — *conveying Falcon's reply*
> "Thank you, yes?"

**Vukradin** — *satisfied*
> "Alright. Okay, we can go."

**Wade Brown** — *questioning whether it was enough*
> "Sort of. I mean, you got, like, two words. He has to apologize before we go charging in, right?"

**GM** — *confirming the apology was unambiguous*
> "No, it was a yes. It was a thank you and yes. Do you apologize? He said, I apologize."

> "He's categorical, unambiguous about his apology."

**Vukradin**
> "Yep, I'm cool with that."

**GM** — *adding Falcon's other information*
> "He says a few more things. He says that he's not in Phandalin, he's on the road home. He hopes to see you there."

