> "You've got… The tattered note, right? Which you should… which is… which is marked. You've got the comment from somebody saying, well, if the first ritual doesn't succeed, the second ritual will be used. Right? The third thing, the second ritual, and the third ritual fails, whoever's in charge will summon the monster, whatever, will summon whatever himself."

> "The thing that's confusing to you is why would they want, like, wasn't the Falcon's Hunting Lodge supposed to be… Controlled by the Talosian, so why would they want to go destroy it?"

