**[Depleted Spell Slots, Lightning Resistance, and the Two-Hour Walk]**

**Vukradin** — *raising the spell slot concern*
> "I'm okay heading over there. He said he's gonna meet us there?"

> "Yeah, but I'm gonna need some better spells."

