**[Resolving to Head to the Lodge]**

**Vukradin** — *assessing urgency*
> "Well, I mean, if the lodge is in danger, and they're gonna summon something, and it's urgent, then no, we shouldn't do that. We'll just have to make do with… with fewer spells."

**GM** — *clarifying uncertainty about timing*
> "I want to be precise. You do know that the ritual will happen again. You don't know if it will happen today."

**GM** — *after the checks*
> "So, some… So whoever's going to do it, then… the other option is to go to the other place. Okay, so to the lodge."

**Vukradin** — *finalising the decision*
